This map was originally made as an aim map named: Aim_Skoutz; (Original I know ;D) It was the first map I had made which included a working sky-box that I will probably upload at some stage.

This map has a HDR Issue where people has glowing guns in some areas, but other then that; I think its a pretty good GG map.

Please give me critique so that I can work on improving this map, thank you. 

-Alex

P.S. I already know about the some of the backwards textures =]
